<! [CDATA[
Batelco Logo
Bahrain Telecommunication Company BSC, trading as Batelco, is the principal telecommunications company in Bahrain. The company’s headquarters are in Bahrain and the company is listed on the Bahrain Bourse. The Chairman of the Board is Abdulla Bin Khalifa Al Khalifa. It provides services for mobiles through UMTS 2100 and LTE 1800 while its residential Internet is an ADSL, Wireless or FTTH service. Batelco is one of Bahrain’s five Internet service providers.
You can download theBatelcologo on full-version of the page.
